  • public class MyConfig
extends com.jfinal.config.JFinalConfig
    This class is for configuration, everything related to this system is configured here such as database connection pool. data tables mapping, page routing, plugins, handlers Also, some variables are initialized here after web started NOTE: RUN this class as Java Application, you can start the website
